Protocol: ISOSK2PMAP AnB 
# The original protocol ISOsymKeyTwoPassMutualAuthProt has a reflection attack 


Types: 

	Agent A,B;
    Number NA,NB,Text1,Text3;
    Function [Agent,Agent ->* SymmetricKey] shk

Knowledge:

    A: A,B,shk(A,B);
    B: B,A,shk(A,B);

Actions:

    A -> B: {|NA,B,Text1|}shk(A,B)
    B -> A: {|NB,A,Text3|}shk(A,B)

Goals:

    A  authenticates B on Text3
    B  authenticates A on Text1